"""
    Get all service Objects and check if created service is present
    """
api = Icinga2API(username=constants.username, password=constants.password,
    url=constants.url, debug=False)
response = api.services.objects()
assert any(result['attrs'].get('name', None) == constants.TestService_name for
    result in response)
pytest.mark.run(order=6)
